txt.en: Fleeing from their defeat at the Battle of the Pelennor Fields, deadly Wargs have taken over Galdir's Dell. They must be driven out, lest they grow in number and threat.
Defeated many Wargs at Galdir's Dell.
You have defeated many Wargs at Galdir's Dell and aided in the renewal of Gondor.
